Register a new user
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"username": "testuser", "email": "test@example.com", "password": "password123"}'

Login to get a token
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"username": "testuser", "password": "password123"}'

Set token as a shell variable
TOKEN="your_jwt_token_here"

to get user's profile /me 
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me

User Routes:
Get all users
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/users

Get sepecific user
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/users/1

Update profile i.e. ID 1
curl -X PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/1 \
-H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"first_name": "Test", "last_name": "UserUpdated"}'

Devices

Create an new device
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/devices \
-H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"name": "Pacemaker 5000", "manufacturer": "MedTech", "model": "PM5K", "is_mri": false, "type": "Cardiac"}'

Get all devices
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/devices

Get a specific device i.e. ID 1
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/devices

Delete a specific device i.e. ID 1
curl -X DELETE -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/devices/1

Admin Routes

Register an admin user
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"username": "adminuser", "email": "admin@example.com", "password": "password123", "role": "ADMIN"}'

Login as admin user
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"username": "adminuser", "password": "password123"}'

Set shell variable
ADMIN_TOKEN="your_admin_jwt_token_here"

Access an admin only route
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $ADMIN_TOKEN" http://localhost:3000/api/admin